m_source=brandnew&#038;utm_campaign=22jun\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/sponsored_float_02.jpg\" alt=\"Float is a Resource Planning Tool used by the World&amp;apos;s Top Creative Teams\" \/><\/a>\n<\/figure>\n<h6>Manage your resource capacity and avoid burnout<\/h6>\n<p>At a glance, see who&#8217;s overworked and who can take on new tasks. Plan for future hires and manage your project pipeline by forecasting your team&#8217;s capacity based on a real-time resource schedule.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"full\">\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.float.com\/?utm_source=brandnew&#038;utm_campaign=22jun\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/sponsored_float_03.jpg\" alt=\"Float is a Resource Planning Tool used by the World&amp;apos;s Top Creative Teams\" \/><\/a>\n<\/figure>\n<p>Teams save at least four hours a week planning their projects and scheduling their resources with Float. Try a free 30 day trial at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.float.com\/?utm_source=brandnew&#038;utm_campaign=22jun\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Float.com<\/a>.<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Rated the #1 resource management software on G2, the world&apos;s top creative teams, including BuzzFeed, Ogilvy, and MetaLab, use Float to plan their projects and schedule their team&apos;s time. Plan for multiple projects on the go See who&apos;s working on&#8230;","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"episode_type":"","audio_file":"","duration":"","filesize":"","date_recorded":"","explicit":"","block":"","filesize_raw":""},"categories":[27],"tags":[620,1841,1842],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8863"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsider